text: Rottach (also: Große Rottach) is a river of Bavaria, Germany. It is a left tributary of the Iller at Kempten. Note that there is another river also called Rottach 18 kilometres upstream which is a right tributary of the Iller. ==See also== *List of rivers of Bavaria ==References== Category:Rivers of Bavaria Category:Rivers of Germany
title: Rottach (Iller, Kempten)
